{"tid":2025000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白衫黑警被問點解朋友聚會遲到，答「大sir永無遲到，係你班友早到！」","createTime":"2020-05-20T03:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T03:14:02.000Z","uid":321059,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d45a60f2dfea5cac53d94f7bc93be9517030c737","tid":2025000,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"有一次老友聚會，明明約7點，但他遲了一小時才到達，我於是笑他：「阿sir做咩遲大到？」<span style=\"color: red;\">豈料這番話卻觸動他的警察神經，正色說：「大sir永無遲到，係你班友早到！」<br />\n</span><br />\n那是老友聚會，全場靜晒，他也許感到氣氛尷尬，於是主動打圓場說：「職業病發作，唔好意思。」<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n由於下屬會對上司的錯視而不見，上司也包庇下屬，當階級差異如此分明，利益之間卻如此緊扣，<span style=\"color: red;\">整個警察部就成為了一個極大染缸。但這個染缸與別的辦公室染缸完全不一樣，因為他們擁有槍，是執法者，他們很難面對制衡。</span>這也是為什麼要有ICAC，因為警權過大，對治理者也是非常頭痛的問題。<br />\n<br />\n全文在此<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200519/UDANOREDECAUUD7YFLJHMRVSB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200519%2FUDANOREDECAUUD7YFLJHMRVSB4%2F&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=a9799cde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200519%2FUDANOREDECAUUD7YFLJHMRVSB4%2F&h=30a9d0b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200519/UDANOREDECAUUD7YFLJHMRVSB4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為有永遠唔會犯錯嘅黑警<br />\n所以就有永遠唔會道歉嘅黑警"},{"pid":"371b24c5a11d8ff529bb90b8d5b18bdce30d2b4e","tid":2025000,"uid":125168,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:22:46.000Z","msg":"個班老友仲真心同黑警fd到都藍到發光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7ab930bb716f6b6846941ebdbab747d916949b","tid":2025000,"uid":297949,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"仲做到朋友即係都係屎啦"},{"pid":"a4a4ac58b3749b4f2a2cf5e0c004794aaf5312e5","tid":2025000,"uid":14454,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03